pageContext.claim: “So General Flynn lies to the FBI and his life is destroyed, while Crooked Hillary Clinton, on that now famous FBI holiday “interrogation” with no swearing in and no recording, lies many times...and nothing happens to her? Rigged system, or just a double standard?”
pageContext.analysis: In regards to Hillary Clinton's testimony under oath about her email practices, FBI Director James Comey told Congress there was "no basis to conclude she lied to the FBI."
